{"title_page": "Junki Hata", "text_new": "{{Infobox football biography\n|name=Junki Hata <br> \u7551\u6f64\u57fa\n|image=\n|image_size=\n|caption=\n|fullname=Junki Hata\n|birth_date={{Birth date and age|1994|8|14}}\n|birth_place=[[Aichi Prefecture|Aichi]], [[Japan]]\n|death_date=\n|death_place=\n|height={{Height|m=1.79}}\n|position=[[Forward (association football)|Forward]]\n|currentclub=[[V-Varen Nagasaki]]\n|clubnumber=29\n|youthyears1 = 2013\u20132016 | youthclubs1=[[Tokai Gakuen University]]\n| years1 = 2016\u2013 | clubs1 = [[V-Varen Nagasaki]] | caps1 = 10 | goals1 = 1\n| years2 = 2018 | clubs2 = \u2192 [[Azul Claro Numazu]] (loan) | caps2 = 25 | goals2 = 8\n|club-update=6 January 2019\n}}\n\n{{Nihongo|'''Junki Hata'''|\u7551 \u6f64\u57fa|Hata Junki|born August 14, 1994}} is a [[Japanese people|Japanese]] [[Association football|football]] player.<ref>[https://data.j-league.or.jp/SFIX04/?player_id=19686 J.League Data Site]</ref> He plays for [[V-Varen Nagasaki]].\n\n==Club statistics==\n''Updated to 23 February 2018''.<ref>Nippon Sports Kikaku Publishing inc./\u65e5\u672c\u30b9\u30dd\u30fc\u30c4\u4f01\u753b\u51fa\u7248\u793e, [https://www.amazon.co.jp/J1-J3%E9%81%B8%E6%89%8B%E5%90%8D%E9%91%91%E3%83%8F%E3%83%B3%E3%83%87%E3%82%A3%E7%89%88-2018-NSK-MOOK/dp/4905411521 \"J1&J2&J3\u9078\u624b\u540d\u9451\u30cf\u30f3\u30c7\u30a3\u7248 2018 (NSK MOOK)\"], 7 February 2018, Japan, {{ISBN|978-4905411529}} (p. 251 out of 289)</ref><ref>Nippon Sports Kikaku Publishing inc./\u65e5\u672c\u30b9\u30dd\u30fc\u30c4\u4f01\u753b\u51fa\u7248\u793e, [https://www.amazon.co.jp/2017-J1-J3%E9%81%B8%E6%89%8B%E5%90%8D%E9%91%91-NSK-MOOK/dp/4905411424/ref=pd_sim_14_1/356-9491148-0114816?_encoding=UTF8&psc=1&refRID=BA8BN4Y0F97GNWKQM78H \"2017 J1&J2&J3\u9078\u624b\u540d\u9451 (NSK MOOK)\"], 8 February 2017, Japan, {{ISBN|978-4905411420}} (p. 213 out of 289)</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! colspan=3 | Club performance\n! colspan=2 | League\n! colspan=2 | Cup\n!